290 to 386 million dollars) annually for building farm-to-market
roads, desalting canals, lining of water courses, construction of
culverts, ponds and soil conservation in low-income rural areas.
</P>
<P>
In the poorest urban areas, schemes of water supply, garbage
collection and sewerage will also be included in the program,he
said.
</P>
<P>
Since he came to power in a bloodless coup on October 12,
General Musharraf has vowed to revitalize the weak economy of the
South Asian country. 
