<HEADLINE> Annan Urges Efficient Peacekeeping in Africa </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
This is because regional organizations in Africa do not have
necessary resources, he told a Council session discussing "the U.N.
partnership with Africa".
</P>
