<HEADLINE> India Rejects Pakistan's Claim On Troops Withdrawal </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NEW DELHI, December 16 (Xinhua) -- India Thursday termed as "an
exercise in obfuscation" Pakistan's claim that it had completed
the withdrawal of additional troops from the line of control (LOC)
in the disputed Kashmir.
</P>
<P>
