Steering Committee, said that it is a positive step forward in
resolving a long, complex and very difficult problem.
</P>
<P>
The agreement provides that in exchange for their existing debt,
banks will be offered a package of instruments including notes
from Dongshen Water Supply Company injected in Guangdong
Investment, various debt instruments of GDE companies, real estate
and equity participation in certain related companies.
