<HEADLINE> India Gets Ready to Deal with Y2K Problem </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
P.V. Jayakrishnan, secretary of the Ministry of Information
Technology, said Thursday that the government has also directed
banks to provide hard copies of accounts statements to people if
demanded.
