<HEADLINE> Weather Forecast for Major Chinese Cities </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, December 16 (Xinhua) -- Weather forecast for 15 major
Chinese cities for the next 24 hours from 20:00 today to 20:00 on
December 17, issued by China's Central Meteorological Station this
evening:
</P>
<P>
Beijing: min. -8 degrees C., max. -1 degree C., clear to cloudy,
calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Shenyang: min. -18 degrees C., max. -10 degrees C., clear, calm
to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Tianjin: min. -7 degrees C., max. 1 degree C., cloudy to clear,
calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Xi'an: min. -2 degrees C., max. 10 degrees C., clear to cloudy,
calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Chengdu: min. 4 degrees C., max. 13 degrees C., cloudy to
overcast, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Chongqing: min. 8 degrees C., max. 12 degrees C., overcast to
cloudy, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Kunming: min. 5 degrees C., max. 18 degrees C., clear, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Nanjing: min. 0 degree C., max. 8 degrees C., overcast to
cloudy, fresh to strong breeze.
</P>
<P>
Shanghai: min. 4 degrees C., max. 10 degrees C., drizzle to
overcast, moderate to fresh breeze.
</P>
<P>
Wuhan: min. 7 degrees C., max. 14 degrees C., cloudy, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Hangzhou: min. 6 degrees C., max. 10 degrees C., drizzle to
overcast, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Taipei: min. 13 degrees C., max. 18 degrees C., drizzle, calm
to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Guangzhou: min. 12 degrees C., max. 15 degrees C., drizzle to
modest rain, gentle to moderate breeze.
</P>
<P>
Hong Kong: min. 13 degrees C., max. 16 degrees C., moderate
rain, gentle to fresh breeze.
</P>
<P>
Macao: min. 13 degrees C., max. 16 degrees C., moderate rain,
gentle to fresh breeze.  
</P>
</TEXT>
