advancing eight cents to 23.05 Australian dollars while ANZ closed
steady at 11.48 Australian dollars, Westpac eased 1.5 cents to 10.
645 Australian dollars and the Commonwealth fell two cents to 25.
49 Australian dollars.
</P>
