systems" initiated by the late Chinese leader Deng Xiaoping is
very wise. The policy, which successfully solved the issue of Hong
Kong's return to China two years ago, will soon solve the issue of
Macao's.
</P>
<P>
He noted that the policy of "one country, two systems", which
has ensured Hong Kong's stability and prosperity after its return
to China, will also be a success in Macao.
</P>
