Province made 14.9 billion yuan in profit, up 28.7 percent over
the same period of 1998.
</P>
<P>
Their net profit reached 3 billion yuan, 1.51 billion yuan more
than the same 1998 period, or up 100.7 percent.
</P>
<P>
